Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在哪裡 金普利先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和之前說的不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說我們進攻的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里克斯肯定會出現叛徒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓倒性勝利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血之紋章
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.74,0:02:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊丹術要讀取龍脈的流向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不知道那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓感覺變得敏銳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三 來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我理論上的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs60}（就是這樣啦）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\an8}（這樣不明白）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 讓我們藏身在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:02:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也得到了幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們的玩耍對象增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴贊帕諾 我們去山上採木材
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被整慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊帕諾那傢伙去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.64,0:03:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 贊帕諾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}螞蟻的一咬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳似乎知道傑利姆的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的真面目也知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國家的領袖和兒子是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳作為一個國民是什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連信任的家人也是虛構的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是很悲傷的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是家族遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模仿了被你們嘲笑為愚者的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 那是上面給我的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統的地位和部下也全部是上面給的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 就是權力者遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 妻子是我自己選的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:04:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生 原來你是那個第五研究所的大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,談不上偉大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有幾名部下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家現在都在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上認識的流亡者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是想讓醫生看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了 贊帕諾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹩腳戲就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方 你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾蟲們 想從我們手心裡逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊帕諾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹩腳戲就到此為止了 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一開始的目的就是把你引誘到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你這性格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦知道我還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會親自追來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三隻垃圾能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管聚集幾個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾還是垃圾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地雷式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊金術也在天天進化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能有那種鍊金術…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是地雷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟著你們的腳步就不會中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它只對人造人起反應
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為雪的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.57,0:07:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道什麼地方有地雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我們這些渣子和垃圾玩弄的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被騙了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是普通的遠端鍊成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物就要像個廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖聽話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾和渣子們別太得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險 好險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥豬動作還挺快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看垃圾和渣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種無聊的攻擊怎麼可能有效
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這個如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則一下扭斷他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得教訓一下才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了吧 醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果幹了多餘的事 我就消滅一個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你幹那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要抵抗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把那個貧民窟做掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是做掉也不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶幾個人去中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為賢者之石的材料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在那裡讓他們做那種東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把研究者們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的部下放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們全都變成賢者之石了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連 連我的部下都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？我沒說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今沒必要悲傷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想想你之前做了多少個賢者之石了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我犧牲了大量人類的性命製作了賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比這個國家的任何人都更清楚賢者之石的製作方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道製作方法就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也知道破壞的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是醫生他們所在的山丘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…這種
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恩維…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能被你們這些下等生物幹掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連合成獸都…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看…看我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別藐視我 人類
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:11:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是被這種東西所玩弄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們贏了 馬可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬可先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傷是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我不知不覺的時候你們幹了這麼大的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你反抗人類才會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這 你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬可先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼做這麼亂來的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以來都是叫我做什麼就做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就這件事想給自己做個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己考慮 自己決定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像妳的雙親那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是別亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤基先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的身體就由我拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不聽使喚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用 沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你們這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想救他的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 隨你喜歡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤基先生 真是短暫的相識
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷疤主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人是站在我這邊的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要轉移視線
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙不是同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別幹沒用的事情 恩維
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經沒空管這麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妨礙我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連同那個男人的身體一起毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演技不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛張聲勢不是我的強項
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不再是我的朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕交了 斷緣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 差不多該把你們的計劃告訴我們了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說 快說 你這蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 弄死它 贊帕諾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了之後就會被殺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會說 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:14:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 鋼之小不點不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該在布里克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是聽說他失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 詳細說說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在巴茲庫爾礦道塌方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣 騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回巴茲庫爾一趟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.85,0:15:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候換作哥哥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會相信對方平安無事繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我們也繼續前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我暫時離隊做點別的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段時間開始考慮的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能一直憎恨這個否定了伊修瓦爾的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了改變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了那個目的 馬可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變這個國家…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也有個城市想去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫里奧爾的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果預想的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡也應該有隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs60}（所以破壞那裡也許是最快的方法）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 妳拿著這個回到妳的國家去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs60}（讓他們的計劃變緩）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs60}（在這期間解明逆轉鍊成陣的構造）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說這也是殺也殺不死的人造人最後的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs60}（逆轉鍊成陣就是指之前看到的那幅畫吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來說不定能救你們一族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我回去了 鍊丹術的事情就不知…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs60}（是的）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是考慮別國的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是抱著這點覺悟來到這個國家的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果權力鬥爭失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳能對把命運寄託在妳身上的人們說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因為顧著別國而沒能拯救他們」 能這麼解釋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家的人會想辦法解決
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常…感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 保重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊丹術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等這裡告一段落了 我還會去向妳學的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅…梅…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 真的非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古利德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊茲米·卡迪斯和丈夫去旅遊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什麼時候才會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回布拉德雷大總統那裡報告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布拉德雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走吧 古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓別的人過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟著他們去的話 就能見到古利德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能挪開妳的腳嗎 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡該叫我少將
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是老樣子一副沒出息的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之…之前的德拉古馬戰是壓倒性勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是讓國土鍊成陣完成了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在對我們來說應該保護的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家的安寧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是威脅這個國家的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須用壓倒性的力量把他們完全擊敗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真是非常勇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話到什麼時候都嫁不出…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的爭鬥心太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你在一起的話 膽小的毛病會傳染的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在這裡嗎 少將
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位是弟弟吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想認他是弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從伊修瓦爾逃回來的膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有東西想讓妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道國家鍊金法的三大限制嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得違背軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得製造金子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得製造人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不得違背軍隊」不用多說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不得製造金子」是為了避免經濟混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼「不得製造人」呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼國家禁止製造人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為倫理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊金術師之間也有因為是對神的褻瀆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而作為默認的規則禁止了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫理是會隨著時代以及個人而改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是因為那種理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了防止個人擁有強大的軍隊 少將
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.51,0:23:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可…真慘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方有地方吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.66,0:23:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得 確實是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅賽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.82,0:23:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還精神吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾才是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 你還在旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 是熟人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.12,0:23:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾 愛德呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.12,0:23:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥…哥哥今天不在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.15,0:23:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.77,0:23:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想見他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.03,0:23:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.01,0:23:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.11,0:23:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我在想那個微妙的表情是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 羅賽 鍋子洗完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.18,0:23:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:24:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會 復活 決意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒靈魂的時候到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.51,0:24:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要還活著 人就會不斷前進
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.07,0:24:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論那是條多麼痛苦的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.48,0:24:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.14,0:24:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第44話 完全恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.32,0:24:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒吧 人類
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.93,0:24:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是 開始的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.40,0:01:24.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}無止境的旅途中  止步不前之時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:31.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}我們深深地歎氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:38.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}再次放開了緊握的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:46.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}但是現在已經沒有什麼可怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:54.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}連接心靈之間那堅固的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:59.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}決不會被斬斷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:09.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}繼續尋求 終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:15.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在這個地方畫上句號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:24.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}悲傷與憤怒 化為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:29.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}命運就在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:50.54,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}本是沒有交點的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:51.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:56.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}企圖奪走我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:22:01.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即使獲得了想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.76,0:22:02.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼卻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:07.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}無法坦率地會心一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:13.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}流出的眼淚    不代表弱小或後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:18.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}只是孕育痛苦的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:23.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不論什麼樣的瞬間與命運
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.30,0:22:32.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}終於明白了唯一可以確定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:34.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}極限也好  困難也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:38.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都不願意放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:43.48,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就這樣決不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:51.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}緊握你的右手傳來的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:54.98,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,750)\blur2}就在這裡


